snippet.title: I remade Pong but it will make you cry
snippet.description:
Enter a new age of walking simulators where we do away with all of that tiresome walking about just let you sit down and talk to a computer while playing GENERIC VIDEO TENNIS.

Download for free: https://danielfoutz.itch.io/videotennis
More Patricia Taxxon music: https://patriciataxxon.bandcamp.com/
